items.title: Awesome Zsh Plugins
items.content_text:
### Themes / [superconsole](https://github.com/alexchmykhalo/superconsole) - Windows-only

*   [jmtech (⭐1)](https://github.com/jmaaltech/jmtech-zsh-theme) - Customizable colors and symbols. Includes decorators for `git` status, exit status of last command run, `gpg` signing information and timestamps. Requires a [Nerd Font (⭐59k)](https://github.com/ryanoasis/nerd-fonts) for the `git` status icons.
items.content_html:
